description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20MIN full body pilates workout // intermediate level // no equipment | LIDIAVMERA' from the channel Lidia Mera.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
